WEBVTT

00:15.030 --> 00:16.470
Good morning, everyone!

00:16.470 --> 00:18.280
Good morning!

00:18.540 --> 00:20.630
It's too far to commute.

00:21.020 --> 00:22.050
I loved the fact that the medical zone

00:22.050 --> 00:23.910
was right in front of my tent.

00:23.910 --> 00:26.370
We enjoyed the pigeons every morning.

00:26.370 --> 00:27.620
Wait for me.

00:27.950 --> 00:28.820
Hello.

00:29.440 --> 00:33.110
Don't you feel like this is our first day of work?

00:33.110 --> 00:34.900
-I know.
-Right?

00:34.900 --> 00:39.090
Me too. It's so cold.

00:39.090 --> 00:40.420
Good morning.

00:41.510 --> 00:44.680
We're really back.

00:47.480 --> 00:48.900
Did you have a good sleep last night?

00:48.900 --> 00:50.500
I was in Uruk all night.

00:50.500 --> 00:52.510
Earthquakes and epidemics...

01:05.349 --> 01:07.770
Oh my! Mr. Han!

01:07.770 --> 01:11.440
Thank you for coming all the way down to the first floor to greet us.

01:11.440 --> 01:12.880
Are you guys okay?

01:12.880 --> 01:14.770
Yes, we're fine.

01:17.020 --> 01:18.160
You! Come here!

01:19.039 --> 01:21.039
I'm the one who came to him first, but he's only concerned about Chi Hoon.

01:21.039 --> 01:22.539
Nice scene.

01:22.970 --> 01:26.470
Why didn't you come when I sent you the charter?

01:26.680 --> 01:29.370
Did you know that your mother's been coming to

01:29.370 --> 01:32.979
the hospital every day and harassing me?

01:32.979 --> 01:34.050
How could I know?

01:38.330 --> 01:39.870
Thank you for your hard work.

01:39.870 --> 01:41.070
We're going to pay you

01:41.070 --> 01:41.720
100 percent of your paychecks

01:41.720 --> 01:43.570
as a special bonus. You should all get

01:44.140 --> 01:45.850
a thorough medical checkup.

01:46.890 --> 01:48.650
I have to submit them to his mother.

01:49.380 --> 01:50.900
Okay. Let's get to work.

01:51.570 --> 01:52.500
Dismissed.

01:54.940 --> 01:56.860
Dismissed. You're dismissed as well.

02:10.160 --> 02:12.010
I'm the one who greeted him, but Kang Mo Yeon gets the bouquet.

02:12.010 --> 02:13.130
Nice scene.

02:13.130 --> 02:14.560
How could you?

02:15.200 --> 02:16.800
I sent the charter so you could come back to Korea,

02:16.800 --> 02:19.040
but you weren't on it.

02:19.040 --> 02:20.100
Do you know how much I beat myself up

02:20.100 --> 02:22.840
after sending you there like that?

02:26.930 --> 02:29.420
What was that?

02:30.000 --> 02:31.230
Kang Mo Yeon!

02:34.579 --> 02:36.380
I missed you so much.

02:40.040 --> 02:41.670
All I could see at the moment

02:41.670 --> 02:42.840
was something exploding,

02:42.840 --> 02:44.490
everything falling down.

02:44.490 --> 02:46.270
Things became so chaotic.

02:46.270 --> 02:49.710
My heart was beating fast and I started feeling dizzy.

02:50.980 --> 02:52.120
What is she talking about?

02:52.500 --> 02:53.860
She's talking about the earthquake.

02:53.860 --> 02:54.970
Earthquake?

02:54.970 --> 02:56.750
Not the moment that you fell in love?

02:56.750 --> 02:57.650
Right.

02:58.380 --> 03:00.130
You're the one who spread the rumor about me dating a guy.

03:00.130 --> 03:02.570
By the time I arrived in Korea, everyone knew.

03:03.600 --> 03:04.350
Who was it then?

03:04.350 --> 03:06.830
Does it matter who it was? It's true, isn't it?

03:06.830 --> 03:08.250
Tell me about this guy.

03:08.250 --> 03:10.630
What's it like to date a Special Forces soldier?

03:12.180 --> 03:14.770
Now I know what to do when my car is hanging off on a cliff,

03:14.770 --> 03:16.520
and how to get out of a mine field without getting hurt.

03:16.520 --> 03:17.610
And what to do

03:17.610 --> 03:19.370
when you're wearing a vest rigged with explosives,

03:19.370 --> 03:20.810
and so on.

03:21.610 --> 03:22.960
What is she talking about?

03:23.180 --> 03:24.880
I don't know.

03:24.880 --> 03:25.860
I never thought

03:25.860 --> 03:27.420
I'd experience stuff like that.

03:33.630 --> 03:34.650
Are you happy to be back in Korea?

03:35.440 --> 03:36.820
I'm still a little overwhelmed.

03:38.170 --> 03:39.500
I miss Uruk from time to time.

03:41.190 --> 03:44.350
I don't see any singing pigeons every morning.

03:44.350 --> 03:45.970
You're not here, either.

03:45.970 --> 03:47.610
Do you miss the pigeons

03:47.610 --> 03:49.310
or me?

03:49.690 --> 03:50.920
Peace in Uruk.

03:51.550 --> 03:52.810
That's what I'm talking about.

03:58.230 --> 03:59.770
Has your life become hectic again?

04:00.250 --> 04:01.870
Do you have to go back up to where you were?

04:01.870 --> 04:03.400
No. I'm going to quit.

04:03.400 --> 04:04.500
I'm going to open up my own clinic.

04:04.500 --> 04:06.170
I've already found a building.

04:07.700 --> 04:09.360
How much do you get paid a month?

04:09.360 --> 04:10.960
If I go bankrupt, do you think you can support me?

04:13.700 --> 04:16.209
Hello? Hello.

04:17.760 --> 04:19.899
This is strange. It sounds so distant.

04:20.399 --> 04:23.010
It feels like you and I are far from each other.

04:23.320 --> 04:24.220
I have to go.

04:26.430 --> 04:27.400
If you go bankrupt,

04:27.400 --> 04:28.960
I'll recruit you to Alpha Team.

04:28.960 --> 04:32.110
You don't have to worry about a thing.

04:32.970 --> 04:34.070
You have more experience

04:34.070 --> 04:36.060
than most of the Special Forces soldiers.

04:36.680 --> 04:37.680
Copy that.

04:38.330 --> 04:39.770
I won't go under. Don't worry.

04:40.100 --> 04:41.840
I've crossed a mine field.

04:46.450 --> 04:47.250
I need to tell you something.

04:47.250 --> 04:47.970
Let me go first.

04:47.970 --> 04:48.620
I'm sorry, but...

04:48.620 --> 04:49.520
On that day

04:51.100 --> 04:52.830
in the hotel room,

04:53.960 --> 04:55.210
what I did was wrong.

04:57.940 --> 05:00.180
I thought, given my position, it would be okay for me to act that way.

05:01.090 --> 05:02.220
However,

05:02.670 --> 05:03.990
it didn't work with you.

05:03.990 --> 05:05.740
I was quite shocked, you know.

05:08.590 --> 05:12.620
That means I was the first woman who slapped you?

05:13.390 --> 05:16.020
Wow! You're unbelievable!

05:16.750 --> 05:18.390
Listen to me, Seo Kwon.

05:18.820 --> 05:20.830
Seo Kwon?

05:20.830 --> 05:22.290
I’ve already told you.

05:22.290 --> 05:24.340
That I'd quit as soon as I came back.

05:25.810 --> 05:27.140
Put it this way,

05:27.140 --> 05:28.610
you're not my boss anymore.

05:31.070 --> 05:31.910
Well,

05:31.910 --> 05:35.140
I have no intention of letting you go.

05:35.140 --> 05:37.970
Another option is you quitting your job.

05:41.970 --> 05:44.130
Hand in your letter of resignation.

05:45.180 --> 05:46.600
Do you really have to do this?

05:47.430 --> 05:48.980
How can you be so heartless?

05:48.980 --> 05:50.180
Have you always been heartless like this?

05:50.180 --> 05:51.980
Have you always been pathetic like this?

05:52.110 --> 05:54.880
I want you to accept my resignation.

05:58.659 --> 06:00.280
How rude!

06:00.570 --> 06:02.160
But I love her!

06:02.960 --> 06:04.140
Why?

06:04.140 --> 06:05.340
Why all of a sudden?

06:05.760 --> 06:07.080
You said I could come in and sign the paper.

06:07.080 --> 06:08.930
Why not now?

06:08.930 --> 06:11.020
I'm sorry.

06:11.020 --> 06:12.940
But when you came to talk to us last time,

06:12.940 --> 06:15.270
you were the professor of the VIP ward at Haesung Hospital.

06:15.270 --> 06:18.020
Now you're just a poor doctor

06:18.020 --> 06:19.740
with a doctor's license.

06:20.180 --> 06:23.040
You're basically jobless.

06:24.670 --> 06:27.830
Are you saying that if I quit the hospital

06:27.830 --> 06:29.660
I can't get a loan from you?

06:30.570 --> 06:32.280
Exactly.

06:34.550 --> 06:37.330
What should I do then?

06:38.630 --> 06:40.050
I can't answer that.

06:41.470 --> 06:43.040
Next!

06:46.860 --> 06:48.770
What do you want me to do?

06:48.770 --> 06:51.010
I want you to have a carefree life.

06:52.770 --> 06:55.540
Opening up a clinic won't give me a carefree life.

06:55.540 --> 06:57.659
A lot of clinics go under these days.

06:57.659 --> 07:00.370
Do you want to stay with the army?

07:03.800 --> 07:05.120
Actually,

07:05.120 --> 07:07.500
soldiers don't need serious operations.

07:07.500 --> 07:09.350
I need to diagnose them accurately so that they

07:09.350 --> 07:12.730
won't make their conditions more serious.

07:16.290 --> 07:17.970
A quick diagnosis as a doctor

07:17.970 --> 07:19.460
and understanding the patients as a fellow soldier

07:19.460 --> 07:21.250
are what I'm really good at.

07:21.250 --> 07:22.410
I like my job,

07:22.410 --> 07:24.230
which is a doctor and soldier.

07:24.700 --> 07:26.620
If a good doctor like me leaves the army,

07:26.620 --> 07:28.090
it'd be a national loss.

07:28.770 --> 07:30.070
Don't you think?

07:30.070 --> 07:31.180
You're absolutely right.

07:32.330 --> 07:34.110
I'll keep that in mind.

07:37.330 --> 07:38.730
I'm sorry to interrupt you two lovebirds

07:39.200 --> 07:40.130
but I have news for you.

07:42.810 --> 07:45.600
Why do you have to do that at a time like this?

07:45.600 --> 07:47.330
Because I want to.

07:48.880 --> 07:49.750
Here.

07:52.590 --> 07:54.030
You're being transferred.

07:54.700 --> 07:56.210
Are you talking about Lieutenant Yoon?

07:56.210 --> 07:59.659
Yes. She's coming back to Korea with us.

08:00.390 --> 08:03.430
For real? How did that happen?

08:04.490 --> 08:06.020
Did my father pull some strings?

08:06.020 --> 08:08.520
Why are you bringing up Commander Yoon here?

08:08.520 --> 08:10.370
It's from Commander Park

08:10.370 --> 08:11.240
and I pulled the strings.

08:11.240 --> 08:12.890
You have no strings to pull.

08:12.890 --> 08:14.320
You can barely take care of yourself.

08:14.810 --> 08:16.060
Really?

08:17.010 --> 08:18.240
Do you want to see me canceling your transfer

08:18.240 --> 08:22.030
to prove that I can pull strings?

08:22.720 --> 08:25.210
My girlfriend has just recovered from a plague

08:25.210 --> 08:27.240
and is still quite delirious.

08:27.290 --> 08:29.990
How did you really do it?

08:32.470 --> 08:33.830
She's recovered

08:34.700 --> 08:37.130
but she needs to take it easy for now.

08:37.130 --> 08:38.630
I don't know if it's okay for her to stay here.

08:39.049 --> 08:44.120
Are you saying I should send Lieutenant Yoon home?

08:44.830 --> 08:46.450
Well...

08:46.450 --> 08:50.400
when Lieutenant Yoon was really sick,

08:50.620 --> 08:54.330
you told me to send her to the US Army camp.

08:54.520 --> 08:56.310
If she finds out,

08:58.450 --> 09:00.510
she might feel resentful towards you.

09:02.890 --> 09:03.960
Hey, Yoo Shi Jin!

09:04.440 --> 09:05.860
Let me get this straight.

09:07.830 --> 09:09.600
Are you threatening me now?

09:09.750 --> 09:12.540
If you're trying to threaten me,

09:14.190 --> 09:15.590
it's working.

09:16.320 --> 09:17.770
What should I do now?

09:19.430 --> 09:21.180
If you think of her parents...

09:21.180 --> 09:22.020
Right?

09:22.980 --> 09:25.800
Even if Commander Yoon wants to bring her in,

09:25.800 --> 09:27.700
he might feel awkward doing that, right?

09:27.700 --> 09:29.940
That never crossed my mind.

09:30.190 --> 09:32.190
You're so thoughtful, sir.

09:41.670 --> 09:43.790
Do you miss me that much?

09:43.790 --> 09:45.000
Help!

09:46.390 --> 09:47.490
Where are you?

09:47.690 --> 09:48.690
What's going on?

09:49.560 --> 09:51.250
I can't get a loan.

09:53.240 --> 09:54.470
I threw my letter of resignation in Mr. Han's face

09:54.470 --> 09:57.950
and went to the bank.

09:58.990 --> 10:00.400
But they won't authorize my loan.

10:00.400 --> 10:01.600
What should I do now?

10:01.600 --> 10:03.470
You didn't think about

10:03.950 --> 10:06.680
getting a loan first and then quitting your job?

10:07.380 --> 10:08.610
What?

10:08.610 --> 10:09.910
"What if the bank won't authorize my loan

10:09.910 --> 10:12.450
after I hand in my letter of resignation?"

10:12.810 --> 10:17.020
That never crossed your mind?

10:17.020 --> 10:18.410
Can't you stay there longer?

10:18.730 --> 10:19.610
Don't come to Korea

10:19.610 --> 10:21.380
to see a silly woman like me.

10:21.380 --> 10:22.800
Don't come and just stay there forever.

10:22.800 --> 10:24.210
I wish you a lifetime of happiness.

10:24.210 --> 10:25.560
Bye.

10:27.710 --> 10:28.950
What? Captain Yoo's not coming?

10:29.110 --> 10:30.270
Too bad.

10:30.270 --> 10:32.180
If Captain Yoo or Sergeant Seo were here,

10:32.180 --> 10:33.320
they could've gone to Mr. Han's office

10:33.320 --> 10:34.910
and stolen your letter of resignation.

10:34.910 --> 10:36.680
Why don't you beg for forgiveness?

10:36.680 --> 10:39.320
How can I do that after what I've done?

10:42.500 --> 10:44.680
That means the professor position's available?

10:45.920 --> 10:47.030
Yay! What about your TV show?

10:47.030 --> 10:48.490
Hey! You're unbelievable!

11:05.180 --> 11:07.060
Is something there?

11:08.260 --> 11:09.730
I wish there were.

11:14.650 --> 11:16.410
Why don't we laugh as if it were a joke?

11:16.410 --> 11:17.510
No.

11:17.510 --> 11:18.500
Okay.

11:19.370 --> 11:20.430
All of us from the Uruk medical services team

11:20.490 --> 11:23.210
should see psychiatrists.

11:23.500 --> 11:25.010
Don't blame the earthquake

11:25.010 --> 11:26.550
for your mental instability.

11:26.550 --> 11:28.820
This is serious.

11:28.820 --> 11:29.970
You’ve resigned.

11:29.970 --> 11:31.390
You can't get treatment because you quit.

11:32.650 --> 11:33.770
Do volunteer work

11:33.770 --> 11:35.150
for the rest of your life.

11:35.600 --> 11:38.110
When you did volunteer work, you were glowing and beautiful.

11:39.370 --> 11:42.260
Now I've made up my mind. Thank you.

11:42.510 --> 11:43.620
Bye.

11:43.890 --> 11:46.070
I'm a rather influential figure.

11:46.250 --> 11:47.590
By the way, where are you going?

11:50.290 --> 11:53.620
I've thought about the past eight years that I've spent at Haesung Hospital.

11:53.620 --> 11:55.230
I started as an intern and became a professor.

11:55.230 --> 11:57.360
While I was working here, Haesung Hospital

11:57.360 --> 11:58.180
was my life,

11:58.180 --> 11:58.990
and myself...

11:58.990 --> 12:03.120
Don't act this way, Director Kang.

12:04.270 --> 12:05.550
You're very funny.

12:06.010 --> 12:08.510
You couldn't get a loan without a job?

12:09.260 --> 12:11.730
I'm sorry that I've troubled you, Mr. Han.

12:11.730 --> 12:13.220
If you give me another chance,

12:13.220 --> 12:15.140
I'll do my best for the VIP Ward at Haesung...

12:15.140 --> 12:16.360
You don't need to work for the VIP Ward.

12:16.360 --> 12:18.840
I want you to work in the ER from now on.

12:20.630 --> 12:22.690
The ER?

12:23.730 --> 12:25.640
You hurt my feelings.

12:25.640 --> 12:27.410
I guess I want you to suffer a little.

12:27.410 --> 12:28.680
You'll usually work night shifts, and all the emergency operations

12:28.680 --> 12:30.810
will be assigned to you.

12:30.810 --> 12:32.050
Sounds awful, doesn't it?

12:33.010 --> 12:36.400
Do you think I'm getting my revenge?

12:38.610 --> 12:40.470
Geeze. You're being silly, Mr. Han.

12:40.790 --> 12:42.920
I think the ER is the most important place at any hospital.

12:42.920 --> 12:45.760
I'll gladly work in the ER.

12:46.600 --> 12:47.710
I'm glad to hear that.

12:54.060 --> 12:56.310
If you don't like working in the ER, come to me.

12:56.630 --> 12:57.980
You won't have to work in the VIP Ward.

12:57.980 --> 12:59.710
I'll make you a VIP.

13:04.290 --> 13:08.130
Thank you for showing me so much affection, sir.

13:11.180 --> 13:12.140
He's a traffic accident patient.

13:12.140 --> 13:13.720
The first hospital he was taken to

13:13.770 --> 13:15.270
transferred him to us for surgery!

13:15.270 --> 13:16.540
Be careful with the IV line.

13:17.340 --> 13:18.440
Who's the doctor?

13:18.440 --> 13:20.010
We need to get an order to get an OR.

13:20.510 --> 13:21.470
I'm here.

13:24.130 --> 13:25.310
Go get an OR now!

13:25.310 --> 13:26.090
Yes, ma'am.

13:28.690 --> 13:30.310
- Squeeze more blood in.
- Yes, ma'am.

13:30.310 --> 13:31.300
Put him on another IV line.

13:31.300 --> 13:31.830
Yes, ma'am!

13:31.830 --> 13:32.480
What are you doing

13:32.480 --> 13:33.310
without even wearing a gown?

13:33.310 --> 13:34.150
Tell me about it.

13:34.150 --> 13:34.920
I’m Kang Mo Yeon.

13:34.920 --> 13:37.760
I'm going to be working in the ER from now on.

13:37.760 --> 13:38.840
I'm happy to be working with you guys.

13:40.760 --> 13:41.850
Number 5 OR room is ready.

13:41.850 --> 13:42.650
I’ve called anesthetics chest surgery

13:42.650 --> 13:43.460
and neurosurgery departments.

13:43.460 --> 13:44.560
Send him up right now!

13:44.560 --> 13:45.920
Without a CT scan?

13:45.920 --> 13:47.540
The previous hospital has already done it.

13:47.540 --> 13:49.620
He needs surgery more than a CT scan.

13:49.620 --> 13:50.970
- Yes, ma'am.
- Ms. Choi!

13:50.970 --> 13:51.660
Yes.

13:54.090 --> 13:55.460
What about the VIP Ward?

13:55.510 --> 13:57.640
I was fired.

13:58.060 --> 13:59.100
What about your TV show?

13:59.730 --> 14:00.780
Not yet.

14:01.950 --> 14:03.480
I'll do my best.

14:03.620 --> 14:04.760
What? In the ER?

14:05.390 --> 14:06.630
No. On my TV show.

14:07.550 --> 14:08.960
A three-way collision accident patient is coming in.

14:08.960 --> 14:10.460
They'll be here in five minutes.

14:10.950 --> 14:12.530
What a way of welcoming me to Korea. Let's go!

14:13.070 --> 14:14.880
She's well positioned and healthy.

14:15.400 --> 14:17.090
You're due in two weeks,

14:17.710 --> 14:18.470
right?

14:18.950 --> 14:20.220
Yes. We have ten days left.

14:20.530 --> 14:23.250
I know you're happy to see each other

14:23.250 --> 14:25.580
but you shouldn't sleep together

14:25.580 --> 14:26.940
for a while, okay?

14:30.120 --> 14:31.660
Why aren't you answering me?

14:34.280 --> 14:35.830
- Okay.
- Yes.

14:41.860 --> 14:43.050
Over here.

14:47.450 --> 14:48.330
Don’t worry.

14:48.330 --> 14:49.340
You're trying hard to impress people.

14:49.340 --> 14:51.410
Hello. How have you been?

14:51.410 --> 14:53.160
You met a guy while busy working

14:53.160 --> 14:54.800
in a foreign land.

14:54.800 --> 14:56.340
I heard he's a soldier.

14:56.340 --> 14:58.380
You didn't screw up while I was gone

14:58.380 --> 15:00.400
and do surgery on the wrong patient or something?

15:00.400 --> 15:01.900
You're so funny.

15:01.940 --> 15:04.120
You had a scandal with Mr. Han just before you left

15:04.120 --> 15:05.920
and met a new guy as soon as you got there?

15:06.630 --> 15:09.350
Is that why you got
fired from the VIP Ward?

15:10.580 --> 15:11.640
Dr. Kim.

15:12.380 --> 15:14.110
While working in Uruk for the past month,

15:14.110 --> 15:17.140
I realized something more.

15:17.320 --> 15:19.160
You and I are lucky people.

15:19.550 --> 15:20.550
I want you to be happy.

15:20.980 --> 15:22.620
I want you to become
a good doctor as well.

15:25.740 --> 15:27.200
Don't lecture me.

15:27.200 --> 15:28.510
You gave some preventive shots

15:28.510 --> 15:29.990
and took some photos.

15:29.990 --> 15:32.040
Do you think you're Albert Schweitzer?

15:38.590 --> 15:40.210
Oops! What's wrong with you guys?

15:43.650 --> 15:45.840
I know what you guys are thinking.

15:45.840 --> 15:46.860
Stay alive.

15:47.450 --> 15:49.230
This is the saddest moment of my life.

15:50.650 --> 15:51.650
What's wrong with me?

15:51.650 --> 15:52.790
Why didn't I grab her hair and pull it?

15:52.790 --> 15:53.720
I'm wondering the same thing.

15:54.830 --> 15:56.530
I also have two perfectly good hands.

15:56.530 --> 15:57.860
I should've thrown

15:58.210 --> 15:59.060
my mess tray at her!

16:00.080 --> 16:02.160
I can be somewhat violent at a time like this.

16:04.720 --> 16:06.240
Throw your mess tray at her?

16:09.770 --> 16:11.610
What's wrong with Dr. Kim?

16:12.100 --> 16:13.240
She's so immature.

16:13.240 --> 16:15.540
She's lucky in a way.

16:17.100 --> 16:18.730
If I'm born again,

16:18.730 --> 16:20.540
I want to be just like her

16:20.540 --> 16:22.190
and live a carefree life.

16:22.560 --> 16:23.360
What about me?

16:23.740 --> 16:24.840
What should I be born again as?

16:26.270 --> 16:27.600
Dr. Song.

16:27.600 --> 16:29.550
You shouldn't get involved with me

16:29.550 --> 16:31.320
and live a happy life.

16:37.000 --> 16:39.280
I wired money to your account.

16:39.280 --> 16:41.060
I have sent you some extra

16:41.060 --> 16:42.180
since I got a bonus this month.

16:42.180 --> 16:44.040
Are you still paying it?

16:44.040 --> 16:45.620
I thought you'd already paid it off.

16:45.620 --> 16:47.960
Next month is the last one.

16:49.330 --> 16:51.980
Thanks to you, I can pay my sister's tuition.

16:52.670 --> 16:54.580
When is she going to graduate?

16:55.180 --> 16:56.690
She's been mooching off of you her whole life.

16:56.690 --> 16:57.760
Isn't she getting a job?

16:59.620 --> 17:02.020
As a person who lent her tuition money...

17:02.020 --> 17:04.869
I won't take your money and run.

17:05.440 --> 17:06.450
Let's go.

17:14.700 --> 17:15.470
Sir.

17:26.180 --> 17:27.420
What are you doing?

17:28.440 --> 17:29.150
They're getting prettied up

17:29.150 --> 17:30.620
before going home.

17:31.140 --> 17:33.260
You stupid idiots!

17:33.260 --> 17:34.530
Are you talking to me?

17:35.880 --> 17:36.900
No, sir!

17:38.330 --> 17:40.560
It hasn't been ten minutes yet.

17:43.110 --> 17:44.360
Come over here and lie down.

17:44.750 --> 17:45.820
You haven't seen your wife

17:45.820 --> 17:47.010
for over six months.

17:47.010 --> 17:48.650
For a married man like me,

17:48.650 --> 17:50.110
history is made

17:50.640 --> 17:52.150
when the lights are off.

17:53.790 --> 17:56.070
Your daughter should look like your wife.

17:56.070 --> 17:58.170
We wish you good luck.

17:58.580 --> 18:00.530
What if his daughter looks like him?

18:02.020 --> 18:03.570
You two, come over here.

18:04.360 --> 18:05.910
Well, we...

18:05.910 --> 18:07.650
We'll do our last round of patrol.

18:07.650 --> 18:08.390
Sir!

18:08.390 --> 18:09.950
Stop right there.

18:13.990 --> 18:15.960
I'll go. You two get some rest.

18:15.960 --> 18:16.700
I need some fresh air.

18:16.700 --> 18:18.500
It hasn't been ten minutes yet.

18:18.500 --> 18:22.490
I'll give you the remaining five minutes.

18:22.490 --> 18:24.220
Tap it on your face so that it gets absorbed.

18:27.470 --> 18:28.910
Teach him how to do it.

18:31.160 --> 18:32.070
Thank you, sir.

18:32.070 --> 18:33.490
Thank you.

18:41.940 --> 18:45.220
You need to leave the army. I want you to find a job at my family company.

18:45.220 --> 18:46.300
Think about it

18:46.810 --> 18:49.840
until you finish your mission here

18:49.840 --> 18:52.860
and decide before you go back to Korea.

18:53.860 --> 18:55.580
If you're going to let her go

18:57.090 --> 18:59.500
or become a man who's suitable for her.

19:02.510 --> 19:04.730
It looks like you're thinking about me.

19:06.740 --> 19:07.950
This is my everyday face.

19:08.970 --> 19:10.270
I think about you every day.

19:11.460 --> 19:13.730
Huh? You're being so sweet.

19:15.200 --> 19:16.790
Why are you here instead of getting some rest?

19:17.690 --> 19:19.180
I'm bored.

19:22.430 --> 19:25.320
Don't stand. Come and sit here.

19:28.750 --> 19:30.130
Aren't I as light as a feather?

19:31.050 --> 19:33.050
I lost weight over the past few days

19:33.050 --> 19:34.110
while I was sick.

19:34.110 --> 19:35.550
And my waist is really slim.

19:35.550 --> 19:36.650
Stop being silly.

19:37.020 --> 19:38.250
Put your hand here.

19:41.990 --> 19:43.850
Opening the present?

19:43.850 --> 19:44.950
You're never going to do it.

19:46.580 --> 19:48.820
Move. I don't want to see you.

19:48.820 --> 19:50.400
If I move, the sun will hurt your eyes.

19:51.210 --> 19:53.020
People might think that you really cared about me.

19:54.930 --> 19:56.320
I love you, Yoon Myung Joo.

20:02.300 --> 20:06.170
Are we breaking up or something?

20:08.660 --> 20:10.160
Are we really breaking up?

20:12.640 --> 20:13.770
I love you.

20:15.420 --> 20:17.000
Very much.

20:18.290 --> 20:19.920
And I will love you forever.

20:20.650 --> 20:22.630
You've broken up with me often because you loved me.

20:25.310 --> 20:26.640
We're not breaking up.

20:27.120 --> 20:28.890
I won't let that happen.

20:35.560 --> 20:38.390
Move! I can't open my eyes.

21:47.300 --> 21:50.350
Four soldiers and Captain Yoo Shi Jin

21:50.350 --> 21:51.440
finished their term

21:51.440 --> 21:52.890
in the Taebeak Unit in Uruk

21:52.890 --> 21:55.820
and were ordered to return to Alpha Team

21:55.820 --> 21:57.200
of the Special Warfare Command.

21:59.070 --> 22:00.780
Salute the Vice Commander!

22:01.220 --> 22:02.440
Sir!

22:02.800 --> 22:03.820
At ease.

22:06.490 --> 22:07.730
Thank you for your hard work.

22:07.730 --> 22:11.120
Commander Yoon is busy overseeing the White Tiger Operation at the moment.

22:11.120 --> 22:13.360
I have his messages for you.

22:13.560 --> 22:15.510
For your three-day leave.

22:15.510 --> 22:18.400
Alpha Team is exempted from all the emergency

22:18.400 --> 22:19.700
from now on.

22:19.700 --> 22:22.800
Leave this camp as soon as possible. Do you understand?

22:22.800 --> 22:23.930
Yes, sir!

22:53.030 --> 22:55.010
16:43 p.m.

22:57.350 --> 22:59.650
To be exact, 72 hours from now.

23:00.800 --> 23:02.020
No excuses.

23:02.350 --> 23:04.120
Don't run away.

23:04.800 --> 23:06.220
- For three days.
- Two nights.

23:16.960 --> 23:17.910
Are you okay?

23:18.050 --> 23:19.100
I'm good.

23:20.100 --> 23:21.740
I'll go get more soju.

23:21.740 --> 23:22.550
Sure.

23:25.720 --> 23:27.190
This phone's acting weird.

23:28.600 --> 23:30.710
No one's answering my calls.

23:32.190 --> 23:34.860
The one who shouldn't answer it did.

23:34.860 --> 23:35.980
Is your wife angry?

23:36.940 --> 23:40.830
Yes. When I turned off the lights, she almost killed me.

23:42.990 --> 23:44.010
How come

23:44.530 --> 23:46.790
no one's answering their phones?

23:47.360 --> 23:49.820
Someone answered and he's here.

23:50.660 --> 23:53.390
This guy is drunk.

23:54.110 --> 23:55.680
I think someone else is drunk.

23:55.680 --> 23:57.440
What the heck

24:07.560 --> 24:09.460
is this mess?

24:09.460 --> 24:10.810
When did they come back?

24:11.180 --> 24:12.430
What took you so long?

24:12.580 --> 24:14.340
I was working the night shift.

24:15.270 --> 24:18.030
Are these guys usually like this?

24:20.720 --> 24:22.540
How did that happen?

24:22.970 --> 24:24.240
This wasn't what I pictured.

24:24.240 --> 24:25.490
I was going to greet him at the airport with a heart-shaped banner.

24:25.490 --> 24:26.830
I bought a new outfit and facial mask as well.

24:27.600 --> 24:29.190
The kimchi stew is really good here.

24:29.190 --> 24:30.100
Would you like a bowl?

24:30.610 --> 24:31.320
Where are you going?

24:31.320 --> 24:32.670
I have to go back to camp.

24:32.670 --> 24:33.970
I'm not on leave.

24:33.970 --> 24:34.960
You can't just ditch me here.

24:34.960 --> 24:36.880
-Take Sergeant Seo!
-Sir.

24:39.250 --> 24:41.100
They're going to drink
for three consecutive days.

24:41.100 --> 24:42.150
I can’t take him.

24:43.420 --> 24:46.550
For how many days? They must be crazy.

24:46.550 --> 24:48.910
Isn't the woman who just walked so pretty?

24:50.370 --> 24:52.540
The woman who went out is prettier.

24:54.430 --> 24:56.920
No. That woman is a lot prettier.

24:59.210 --> 25:01.080
By the way, she's staring at me.

25:01.080 --> 25:02.480
Don't look.

25:03.020 --> 25:04.400
If we start a fight with a civilian,

25:04.400 --> 25:05.360
we'll get in trouble.

25:06.600 --> 25:08.510
Corporal Lee Chi Hoon.

25:14.970 --> 25:16.270
Drink! Drink!

25:16.840 --> 25:17.820
Congratulations!

25:17.820 --> 25:19.780
Cheers!

25:30.890 --> 25:32.160
Wake up!

25:33.680 --> 25:36.520
You're not supposed to sleep.

25:39.260 --> 25:41.660
What are you talking about? I’m awake.

25:46.170 --> 25:47.160
Are you sleeping?

25:48.740 --> 25:49.630
I'm not sleeping.

25:51.570 --> 25:54.220
Auntie, two more bottles of soju, please.

25:55.940 --> 25:59.760
Soju!

25:59.760 --> 26:01.750
I brought some soju.

26:02.350 --> 26:03.500
Thank you.

26:04.890 --> 26:06.530
By the way, what are you doing here?

26:07.560 --> 26:09.380
Tell me about it. Why am I here?

26:09.380 --> 26:11.760
What are you eating by the way?

26:12.160 --> 26:15.020
Almonds. I need stamina.

26:15.020 --> 26:17.180
It's so hard to keep up with these two idiots.

26:17.880 --> 26:18.940
Have some.

26:18.940 --> 26:20.040
Give me some.

26:20.040 --> 26:21.610
I'm getting old.

26:24.170 --> 26:26.120
Huh?The woman we saw yesterday came back.

26:28.720 --> 26:30.990
I think she lives here.

26:32.730 --> 26:35.800
I'm going to talk to her today.

26:37.440 --> 26:38.390
Excuse me.

26:38.920 --> 26:40.210
You're still alive.

26:42.180 --> 26:42.980
Huh? Do you know me?

26:42.980 --> 26:44.540
Of course she does.

26:44.790 --> 26:47.350
She's your girlfriend.

26:47.350 --> 26:49.870
Really? Awesome!

26:50.570 --> 26:52.180
Are you my girlfriend?

26:54.470 --> 26:55.680
She's my girlfriend.

26:57.020 --> 26:58.820
Isn't she really pretty?

26:58.820 --> 27:00.640
What's going on, Sergeant Seo?

27:01.210 --> 27:03.310
You're not drinking?

27:18.340 --> 27:20.410
Oh my! I remember this place.

27:21.030 --> 27:24.150
I really do.

27:24.320 --> 27:28.410
I know. I know. Take your shoes off.

27:29.070 --> 27:29.870
No.

27:29.870 --> 27:33.080
I'm not taking my shoes off in someone's place.

27:33.080 --> 27:34.470
Okay. Take your shoes off and get some rest.

27:34.470 --> 27:36.600
Are you coming on to me now?

27:36.600 --> 27:37.500
I don't eat ramen

27:37.500 --> 27:40.050
at some strange guy's place.

27:40.050 --> 27:43.750
Okay. I'll just take your shoes off. Just your shoes. Stay still.

27:47.110 --> 27:48.060
You're not just drunk.

27:48.060 --> 27:49.070
You're hammered.

27:49.900 --> 27:52.830
I want some chicken and beer.

27:52.830 --> 27:56.400
Let's drink some more.

27:58.440 --> 28:01.420
Order some chicken and beer. Now!

28:01.420 --> 28:03.140
Let's drink some more.

28:05.510 --> 28:07.900
Let's drink some more. Come on.

28:09.530 --> 28:10.130
Hush.

28:10.860 --> 28:12.030
What is it?

28:13.950 --> 28:15.090
Be quiet.

28:35.030 --> 28:36.390
- Mom?
- Mom?

28:37.780 --> 28:38.680
Mom's jacket.

28:39.990 --> 28:41.040
Mom's purse.

28:42.480 --> 28:43.520
My mom.

28:52.690 --> 28:54.530
Who's this young man?

28:56.110 --> 28:57.010
How do you do, ma'am?

28:57.660 --> 28:58.850
I'm Dr. Kang's boyfriend,

28:58.850 --> 28:59.960
Yoo Shi Jin.

28:59.960 --> 29:02.920
My boyfriend? Really?

29:04.550 --> 29:07.650
He's my boyfriend. He's handsome, isn't he?

29:08.110 --> 29:09.520
Why do you always

29:09.520 --> 29:10.930
go all the way when you drink?

29:13.630 --> 29:15.640
She got a drinking problem,

29:15.640 --> 29:17.390
as you can see.

29:17.390 --> 29:18.390
It's okay.

29:18.390 --> 29:19.310
I find her cute.

29:19.940 --> 29:21.730
I'm so glad that you think that way.

29:22.610 --> 29:25.170
By the way, what do you do?

29:25.520 --> 29:27.700
He's a soldier. He's a captain.

29:27.700 --> 29:29.780
But I can't tell you more than that.

29:30.080 --> 29:32.770
It's secret.

29:33.640 --> 29:36.550
Goosebumps! I started to remember something.

29:38.000 --> 29:39.830
A paycheck comes in every month

29:39.830 --> 29:41.440
and one wouldn't come home that often.

29:41.440 --> 29:42.240
Not bad.

29:42.240 --> 29:45.810
Mom, don't be too straightforward. You just met him.

29:45.810 --> 29:47.730
I'm talking about you.

29:48.460 --> 29:50.470
She technically lives at the hospital.

29:50.470 --> 29:52.280
Her paycheck comes in every month.

29:54.620 --> 29:57.770
Why are you standing like that?

29:58.470 --> 30:00.250
Did you do something bad?

30:00.540 --> 30:01.380
No, I did no such thing.

30:01.720 --> 30:02.580
You didn't?

30:02.940 --> 30:03.860
Why not?

30:03.860 --> 30:06.390
I'm sorry,
but if you want me to...

30:07.700 --> 30:09.060
That didn't come out right.

30:10.650 --> 30:12.600
You're so naive, Captain Yoo.

30:13.380 --> 30:15.250
Mo Yeon was also

30:15.250 --> 30:16.860
a bookworm.

30:16.860 --> 30:19.620
She hasn't had any boyfriends...

30:19.620 --> 30:23.240
Mom, stop. You're making things worse.

30:23.240 --> 30:24.950
He knows about Yoon Gi

30:24.950 --> 30:26.840
and Mr. Han.

30:27.760 --> 30:28.770
Huh? Goosebumps!

30:28.770 --> 30:31.050
What's this? Why do I remember these things?

30:31.440 --> 30:34.140
I think she should get some sleep. If you'll excuse me.

30:34.530 --> 30:36.330
No, you stay. I'm leaving.

30:36.330 --> 30:37.560
I'm not that old-fashioned.

30:37.560 --> 30:38.640
I'm somewhat old-fashioned.

30:38.960 --> 30:39.760
I have to go.

30:40.690 --> 30:42.740
I'm going to visit you with her.

30:42.740 --> 30:43.810
Okay.

31:00.530 --> 31:03.080
I'm running 10 minutes late. Can you order my sandwich?

31:03.080 --> 31:04.460
A club sandwich.

31:04.460 --> 31:06.610
No onions. Lots of jalapeños.

31:06.610 --> 31:09.580
Lots of hot chili sauce. And toasted white bread.

31:09.580 --> 31:10.500
This is what I want.

31:12.410 --> 31:14.500
Two club sandwiches, right?

31:15.280 --> 31:17.210
How would you like to pay?

31:17.520 --> 31:18.600
With this.

31:19.280 --> 31:20.310
Right.

31:26.010 --> 31:26.950
Have you sobered up yet?

31:27.300 --> 31:29.690
Of course. I didn't drink much.

31:30.780 --> 31:32.070
You did.

31:32.070 --> 31:33.670
When you were drunk, you were weird.

31:33.670 --> 31:35.190
No way.

31:35.550 --> 31:36.400
I'm not that weird.

31:36.400 --> 31:37.410
I remember everything.

31:38.440 --> 31:39.990
I don't believe you.

31:43.880 --> 31:45.270
What did your mother say?

31:46.870 --> 31:48.150
Does she like me?

31:49.400 --> 31:50.620
Did you meet my mother?

31:50.950 --> 31:51.810
When?

31:52.420 --> 31:53.650
You said you remembered everything.

31:54.930 --> 31:55.660
Don't ever drink

31:55.660 --> 31:56.880
with other men.

31:56.880 --> 31:59.920
Are you jealous?

32:01.270 --> 32:02.490
You're still drunk.

32:03.540 --> 32:04.990
Oh, you're smart!

32:06.580 --> 32:07.660
Phone! Phone!

32:15.140 --> 32:15.990
Sir.

32:16.250 --> 32:17.040
Captain Yoo Shi Jin!

32:18.260 --> 32:19.020
Yes, sir.

32:25.070 --> 32:26.240
Yes, sir.

32:26.640 --> 32:28.360
Yes, sir!

32:34.800 --> 32:38.430
I have to go department store now.

32:41.060 --> 32:42.210
Ah?

32:42.210 --> 32:43.150
I'm sorry.

32:49.140 --> 32:49.920
Don't be.

32:52.570 --> 32:54.060
Let's watch a movie when you come back.

32:55.050 --> 32:56.260
Yes or no?

33:00.480 --> 33:01.420
Yes.

33:03.580 --> 33:04.840
Good luck.

33:05.670 --> 33:06.920
Thank you.

33:29.050 --> 33:30.800
You're from the dark side.

33:30.800 --> 33:32.080
You look good in black.

33:32.080 --> 33:33.600
That's because my skin is fair.

33:34.740 --> 33:37.700
Anyway, I like your fair skin.

33:42.370 --> 33:45.460
The briefing starts in one minute. No small talk.

33:45.460 --> 33:46.360
Sir!

33:48.660 --> 33:50.230
What are you doing here?

33:51.600 --> 33:52.910
Are you also part of this operation?

33:52.910 --> 33:54.730
I'm not here to greet you.

33:55.450 --> 33:58.020
I'm the supervisor

33:59.560 --> 34:01.050
of Operation 1029.

34:01.050 --> 34:02.420
What are you doing?

34:02.420 --> 34:03.690
Get in the room! Now!

34:07.370 --> 34:09.210
Check the route for the guests first.

34:09.690 --> 34:11.150
Check your weapons as well.

34:11.580 --> 34:13.949
Your security channel is Number 3.

34:16.929 --> 34:19.090
You know how to use these ballpoint pens.

34:19.090 --> 34:21.320
When you poke
your enemy's carotid artery,

34:21.320 --> 34:23.260
you can kill him within 10 seconds without pain.

34:31.210 --> 34:33.590
Mr. President sends his regards.

34:33.590 --> 34:36.270
Leader Kim sends his regards as well.

34:41.020 --> 34:42.659
Let's go.

34:52.889 --> 34:55.620
How's the cut that I gave you last time?

34:56.050 --> 34:57.190
Sorry about that.

34:59.720 --> 35:01.380
I can't leave empty handed.

35:02.850 --> 35:06.310
As a warrior of my republic, I need to take down

35:06.310 --> 35:08.020
a South Korean soldier to save face.

35:20.300 --> 35:21.350
Have you been working

35:21.350 --> 35:23.160
as a security service agent?

35:23.160 --> 35:24.620
Sorry about that.

35:25.250 --> 35:27.170
You never shut up, do you?

35:31.040 --> 35:32.960
Do you want a rematch right here,

35:32.960 --> 35:35.200
right now without that ballpoint pen?

35:35.690 --> 35:38.910
I don't think you want to write a long report.

35:43.640 --> 35:44.650
I'm not going to give you a break

35:44.650 --> 35:46.530
simply because this is your turf.

35:47.440 --> 35:49.450
You're quite gutsy, aren't you?

35:51.880 --> 35:53.210
Be thankful that you and I are standing and

35:53.210 --> 35:54.880
facing the same direction.

35:55.210 --> 35:56.800
To warriors like us,

35:56.800 --> 35:59.100
looking at the same direction

35:59.100 --> 36:01.470
means a peaceful truce.

36:03.870 --> 36:05.740
Let me ask you one thing as your guest.

36:07.730 --> 36:09.150
Can we eat ice noodles for lunch?

36:09.690 --> 36:12.700
I want to eat
Pyongyang style ice noodles.

36:19.430 --> 36:22.080
Sprinkle vinegar on the noodles

36:22.080 --> 36:25.770
and mix the mustard in the soup before you eat.

36:26.550 --> 36:27.450
Thank you.

36:30.920 --> 36:32.120
Thank you for a delicious lunch.

36:32.120 --> 36:34.060
-Enjoy.
-Enjoy.

36:34.690 --> 36:37.720
By the way, there's something you should know.

36:39.490 --> 36:41.520
Don't listen to the waitress.

36:42.360 --> 36:44.280
In Pyongyang,

36:44.280 --> 36:45.850
you mix mustard with the noodles.

36:50.450 --> 36:52.230
Thank you for your tip.

36:52.230 --> 36:55.590
When you come to Seoul next time, it's my treat.

36:57.660 --> 37:00.180
I'm not going to Seoul.

37:00.780 --> 37:02.550
I'm on leave starting tomorrow.

37:06.860 --> 37:10.580
I'm going to pay you back when I have the chance.

37:12.090 --> 37:14.710
No worries. Just enjoy your lunch.

37:23.330 --> 37:24.980
The door will open.

37:36.350 --> 37:37.810
How's Dr. Kang doing?

37:38.220 --> 37:39.620
Is she complaining about working in the ER?

37:39.620 --> 37:41.610
No. She looks very lively and cheerful.

37:43.260 --> 37:45.450
Are you sending her flowers every day?

37:45.450 --> 37:47.440
Yes, but she sends them back every time.

37:47.870 --> 37:50.050
Thanks to her, my office smells so nice.

37:52.580 --> 37:54.420
Have you found out

37:54.420 --> 37:55.570
about her boyfriend?

37:55.570 --> 37:57.180
That's a little strange.

37:57.180 --> 37:58.440
No one in the army

37:58.440 --> 37:59.800
knows about him.

37:59.800 --> 38:01.480
Other than he's with the Special Warfare Command.

38:01.870 --> 38:03.710
But I got my hands on his picture.

38:06.190 --> 38:07.340
Here. Are you kidding me?

38:08.440 --> 38:09.740
Which one?

38:10.750 --> 38:11.660
I'm not sure yet.

38:11.660 --> 38:12.580
What? Unbelievable!

38:15.440 --> 38:16.860
That's him.

38:16.860 --> 38:19.010
He’s Dr. Kang Mo Yeon's boyfriend.

38:19.010 --> 38:21.430
Born in 1983. Name: Yoo Shi Jin.

38:21.430 --> 38:23.030
Captain in the Korean Army.

38:23.030 --> 38:24.820
Pisces. Blood Type A.

38:26.660 --> 38:28.550
Right.

38:29.170 --> 38:32.020
That's him? By the way, it's him.

38:32.420 --> 38:33.720
If you'll excuse me.

38:37.230 --> 38:38.170
Hold on.

38:41.600 --> 38:42.870
Can you talk to me for a second?

38:44.990 --> 38:47.640
You two gentlemen have a good time.

38:57.260 --> 38:59.420
So, you're Professor Kang's boyfriend...

39:02.530 --> 39:04.340
Is your arm okay?

39:05.390 --> 39:06.410
Are you that confident

39:06.410 --> 39:07.750
or are you pretending?

39:08.370 --> 39:09.810
If Dr. Kang turned me

39:09.810 --> 39:11.310
down over you,

39:11.760 --> 39:13.890
it would hurt my feelings.

39:15.230 --> 39:17.150
Anyway, you're a captain of the Special Warfare Command.

39:19.160 --> 39:20.150
Are you good at fighting?

39:23.120 --> 39:24.530
I heard that

39:24.530 --> 39:25.340
you took my girlfriend

39:25.340 --> 39:28.110
to a hotel room for the first time.

39:31.810 --> 39:33.740
If I were you, I'd be careful.

39:34.120 --> 39:37.950
Day and night. Watch your back.

39:39.810 --> 39:41.180
I'm good at fighting.

39:49.280 --> 39:51.610
Kang Mo Yeon, can you cover for me today?

39:51.610 --> 39:52.730
No.

39:53.160 --> 39:55.630
I'm asking you to cover for me and you said no?

39:55.630 --> 39:57.160
Right.

39:57.610 --> 40:00.230
I'm not the same Kang Mo Yeon who used to cover for you.

40:00.230 --> 40:01.010
Leave me alone.

40:02.150 --> 40:03.080
Hey! You're supposed to cover for anyone

40:03.080 --> 40:04.060
at this hospital.

40:04.060 --> 40:05.180
What's this about?

40:05.480 --> 40:07.930
Yes, I'm supposed to cover for anyone

40:08.130 --> 40:09.250
but I'm not covering for you.

40:12.010 --> 40:13.260
Has the department store already closed?

40:13.630 --> 40:14.720
I finished early to be here

40:14.720 --> 40:15.880
when you got off work.

40:16.760 --> 40:19.040
It's too early for the department store to be closed.

40:19.040 --> 40:20.960
It's not the kind of department store  that you know.

40:20.960 --> 40:21.700
Stay out of it.

40:21.700 --> 40:24.520
I know more about department stores than you do.

40:24.970 --> 40:27.790
By the way, who is he? Can I say hi to him?

40:28.590 --> 40:30.510
You're getting a call. I think it's an emergency.

40:30.510 --> 40:32.290
I don't have a cell phone with me.

40:34.430 --> 40:35.680
I'm Kim Eun Ji,

40:35.680 --> 40:36.870
Dr. Kang's friend.

40:37.590 --> 40:38.620
Nice to meet you.

40:39.650 --> 40:40.920
I'm Yoo Shi Jin.

40:41.360 --> 40:42.600
I'm Dr. Kang's boyfriend.

40:42.600 --> 40:43.520
Nice to meet you.

40:43.520 --> 40:44.960
It's not.

40:46.700 --> 40:49.520
You're her soldier boyfriend from the rumor.

40:50.340 --> 40:51.450
I'm off.

40:52.410 --> 40:53.390
Bye.

40:55.610 --> 40:56.670
How annoying!

40:56.670 --> 40:59.230
How can a soldier be so good-looking?

41:00.940 --> 41:03.170
-Nice to meet you. -Nice to meet you.

41:03.170 --> 41:04.590
There's nothing nice about it.

41:04.590 --> 41:05.970
How crazy!

41:05.970 --> 41:07.200
Are you talking to me?

41:07.200 --> 41:09.690
No. That stupid wench earlier.

41:11.400 --> 41:12.580
The timing's a little strange.

41:12.940 --> 41:14.100
Can't you tell that

41:14.100 --> 41:15.280
we're not that close?

41:15.680 --> 41:17.950
I make sure that you'd know how much I hate her.

41:17.950 --> 41:19.440
Do you have to be nice to her?

41:19.840 --> 41:21.040
You dealt with the

41:21.040 --> 41:22.000
mines shrewdly,

41:22.000 --> 41:23.300
but you're being a little thick at the moment.

41:25.080 --> 41:27.130
Are you jealous or something?

41:28.640 --> 41:30.980
If you knew who I'd just bumped into,

41:31.310 --> 41:32.470
you wouldn't treat me like this.

41:32.470 --> 41:33.680
Who?

41:33.680 --> 41:36.140
-Did you meet the owner of this hospital?
-Yes, I did.

41:36.540 --> 41:37.760
Are you hurt or something?

41:37.760 --> 41:39.470
I was worried.

41:39.470 --> 41:40.680
Have you eaten?

41:40.680 --> 41:42.470
Why didn't you eat dinner?

41:42.470 --> 41:43.710
Let me buy you dinner.

41:45.280 --> 41:46.540
The timing's a little strange.

41:47.310 --> 41:49.240
Look how pretty this fountain is.

41:49.710 --> 41:51.310
Is it rococo?

41:51.680 --> 41:52.810
Stop.

41:52.810 --> 41:54.740
Let's talk about this Mr. Han guy.

41:54.740 --> 41:56.740
Wow! Look at the lamps!

41:57.200 --> 41:59.140
Stop avoiding my question.

41:59.140 --> 42:01.000
What? What do you want me to say?

42:01.000 --> 42:02.390
What are you doing?

42:02.390 --> 42:04.360
I thought I could grab it with my hand.

42:04.360 --> 42:06.000
That's how I measured the size

42:06.000 --> 42:07.140
and I think it'll fit.

42:09.100 --> 42:10.400
I bought you a present.

42:10.400 --> 42:12.470
Did you just measure my neck size?

42:12.470 --> 42:13.080
Just like that?

42:14.450 --> 42:15.540
My hand was

42:15.540 --> 42:18.920
close to your neck, yes.

42:20.400 --> 42:22.430
Dae Young and Myung Joo are waiting.

42:23.320 --> 42:24.580
I don't want to give it to you when they're present.

42:30.800 --> 42:31.770
Pretty.

42:32.670 --> 42:35.740
People usually go "Do you like it?" first.

42:36.030 --> 42:38.050
Right. Do you like it?

42:38.050 --> 42:39.940
Yes. I'm pretty, aren't I?

42:41.670 --> 42:42.610
Pretty good.

42:43.170 --> 42:44.000
Let's go.

42:46.810 --> 42:48.590
I'm not a woman who's easily swayed

42:48.590 --> 42:50.820
by presents like this.

42:50.820 --> 42:53.330
You're not? Why are you smiling then?

42:53.330 --> 42:54.210
I'm not smiling.

42:54.210 --> 42:55.430
Okay.

43:00.570 --> 43:01.800
It's been a while.

43:03.120 --> 43:05.580
You two have new girlfriends now.

43:06.910 --> 43:09.340
They came with a wolf and a rabbit before.

43:09.840 --> 43:10.910
Stuffed animals.

43:11.770 --> 43:12.900
Enjoy.

43:16.900 --> 43:18.910
She is my girlfriend.

43:19.940 --> 43:21.370
She's my fellow soldier.

43:21.640 --> 43:22.660
Fellow soldier?

43:23.360 --> 43:25.610
We fought in Uruk together.

43:25.890 --> 43:27.160
Right.

43:28.970 --> 43:30.570
You two aren't the only people here.

43:31.650 --> 43:33.830
By the way, when did you get here?

43:33.830 --> 43:34.920
What's with the stuffed animals?

43:34.920 --> 43:36.380
Your boyfriend

43:36.380 --> 43:38.730
wanted to get his cell phone

43:38.730 --> 43:39.720
which had your pictures in it, back.

43:39.720 --> 43:41.230
We have to fight 17 guys and we almost died.

43:41.540 --> 43:43.670
It was the hardest battle of my life.

43:43.830 --> 43:45.000
My pictures?

43:45.300 --> 43:46.550
He deleted all my pictures.

43:47.540 --> 43:49.280
I didn't say they were Myung Joo's pictures.

43:49.280 --> 43:50.140
You said it was nothing to be proud of,

43:50.140 --> 43:51.700
but juicy.

43:53.140 --> 43:55.500
Was the fight in front of Haesung Hospital

43:55.500 --> 43:58.090
that I saw in the surveillance footage?

43:59.080 --> 44:00.310
Right.

44:00.310 --> 44:01.950
That's the day we first met.

44:03.640 --> 44:04.830
Stop.

44:06.240 --> 44:07.560
I don't see any pictures of mine.

44:08.150 --> 44:09.760
How could you delete them all?

44:10.130 --> 44:12.860
What the heck are they?

44:14.090 --> 44:15.400
Do you sell used cars

44:15.400 --> 44:16.300
as a second job?

44:17.190 --> 44:20.120
What the heck are these?

44:20.120 --> 44:21.310
Did you drag me into a fight to get these?

44:21.310 --> 44:22.870
They're Myung Joo's pictures to me.

44:23.320 --> 44:24.990
Does my face look yellow to you?

44:28.140 --> 44:29.680
I didn't know how to date

44:29.680 --> 44:31.970
so I always got drunk whenever I met Myung Joo.

44:32.780 --> 44:34.700
I couldn't drive her home

44:34.700 --> 44:36.210
and got her cabs when she left.

44:37.410 --> 44:39.330
Those are the plate numbers.

44:40.390 --> 44:41.740
When we broke up,

44:41.740 --> 44:43.720
I deleted all the pictures that we took together

44:43.930 --> 44:48.710
but I thought I could convince myself that these weren't Myung Joo's pictures.

44:49.240 --> 44:50.390
That's why I kept them.

44:51.700 --> 44:53.760
Sergeant Seo is so cool.

44:55.750 --> 44:57.700
I think I'm falling for you all over again.

45:00.480 --> 45:02.750
You two aren't the only people here.

45:04.020 --> 45:05.250
By the way, how do you know.

45:05.760 --> 45:08.100
Dae Young's phone password?

45:08.720 --> 45:09.920
I made it for him.

45:10.220 --> 45:11.240
He thinks

45:11.240 --> 45:12.570
this is the only password.

45:15.210 --> 45:17.270
When you buy a cell phone,

45:17.270 --> 45:19.160
they give you a booklet.

45:19.160 --> 45:21.930
It has instructions on how to use your phone.

45:21.930 --> 45:23.030
I know.

45:23.430 --> 45:24.220
That's the only

45:24.220 --> 45:25.570
password I know.

45:27.310 --> 45:28.230
Let's go.

45:28.230 --> 45:29.520
Are we still here?

45:33.990 --> 45:35.380
- See you later.
- Apologize.

45:35.740 --> 45:36.890
I'm sorry.

45:36.890 --> 45:39.680
Can't you see we're here?

45:40.460 --> 45:41.790
Don't be that way and have a seat.

45:48.130 --> 45:50.710
Do those pictures mean that much to you?

45:51.260 --> 45:53.690
So nice.

46:02.800 --> 46:05.180
Where are you heading?

46:07.260 --> 46:10.080
Are you taking me home now?

46:10.080 --> 46:11.650
We're both grown-ups.

46:11.650 --> 46:14.070
Grown-ups don't go home early.

46:14.070 --> 46:15.970
You've been abroad. It's time for you to grow up.

46:15.970 --> 46:18.260
How can you be so consistent?

46:18.730 --> 46:20.160
I might not take you home tonight.

46:20.580 --> 46:22.110
That's the spirit.

46:22.940 --> 46:24.360
Shut up

46:24.360 --> 46:25.750
and answer the phone.

46:35.610 --> 46:36.790
Who is it?

46:37.320 --> 46:38.430
Someone I don't know.

46:38.430 --> 46:39.340
I think you know who it is.

46:39.860 --> 46:40.910
No.

46:44.260 --> 46:46.120
Is he Yoon Gi, who bought you chicken ginseng stew?

46:46.120 --> 46:48.190
I can guarantee you that it's not Yoon Gi.

46:48.490 --> 46:51.690
Besides,

46:51.690 --> 46:52.980
I paid with my own money when we ate...

46:58.640 --> 47:01.140
Do you think I bought this car

47:01.140 --> 47:01.940
with that function

47:01.940 --> 47:03.210
so that you could snatch my cell phone?

47:06.630 --> 47:08.930
This is Sergeant Kim Beom Rae.

47:08.930 --> 47:10.800
There was nothing unusual about

47:10.800 --> 47:11.850
Sergeant Seo during afternoon training.

47:11.850 --> 47:13.360
He styled his hair with wax three times

47:13.360 --> 47:14.470
and went out.

47:14.470 --> 47:16.840
I didn't do it three times. It was just two.

47:16.840 --> 47:18.700
Sir! Sergeant Kim Beom Rae.

47:18.700 --> 47:20.960
I'm returning to the camp at 22:00.

47:20.960 --> 47:22.320
Cook ramen for me.

47:22.320 --> 47:23.950
Make the noodles out of you.

47:29.270 --> 47:31.930
Well, it's become a habit.

47:33.150 --> 47:35.430
People don't change overnight, so...

48:04.140 --> 48:05.260
I'm not going to kiss you.

48:07.000 --> 48:08.050
This is your punishment.

48:27.390 --> 48:28.460
Not bad.

48:29.680 --> 48:30.960
By the way, why are the noodles made of flour?

48:32.470 --> 48:33.760
Well...

48:34.050 --> 48:34.990
Kim Beom Rae.

48:34.990 --> 48:36.260
Sergeant Kim Beom Rae!

48:37.000 --> 48:38.910
Are you going to be on my side

48:38.910 --> 48:41.280
or do you want me to turn you into noodles?

48:43.630 --> 48:44.890
Sergeant Seo came back at 20:00.

48:44.890 --> 48:46.420
Came back at 20:00.

48:46.420 --> 48:48.740
At the present hour of 21:00, he's handsome.

48:48.740 --> 48:51.430
At 22:00, he'll still be handsome.

48:51.430 --> 48:54.330
When he goes to sleep, he'll be handsome as well.

48:54.330 --> 48:57.900
That's all.

48:59.560 --> 49:02.020
By the way, Commander Yoon's coming back tomorrow.

49:02.620 --> 49:03.800
Yes. I understand.

49:03.800 --> 49:05.590
Yes, ma'am.

49:14.710 --> 49:15.660
This is my lucky day.

49:22.050 --> 49:23.030
Sir!

49:24.250 --> 49:25.690
I have something to tell you.

49:25.690 --> 49:26.730
I heard.

49:28.080 --> 49:29.320
Let's have some tea. Have a seat.

49:29.560 --> 49:30.960
Thank you,

49:31.410 --> 49:33.150
but can I come back some other time?

49:36.520 --> 49:37.560
Sure.

49:38.930 --> 49:41.680
Can I assume that this is your decision?

49:43.490 --> 49:44.500
What is it?

49:44.500 --> 49:46.670
He's going to retire.

49:51.370 --> 49:52.090
Dad!

49:52.090 --> 49:53.470
Yes, sir!

49:53.790 --> 49:56.330
I'm leaving the army.

49:59.340 --> 50:00.760
Do you have to do this?

50:01.570 --> 50:03.210
Do you have to make him retire?

50:03.260 --> 50:04.600
After what I told you?

50:06.220 --> 50:07.390
Lieutenant Yoon heard

50:07.570 --> 50:09.480
everything we talked about.

50:10.950 --> 50:12.930
While she was sick in the epidemic,

50:12.930 --> 50:15.700
she called me and asked me

50:15.700 --> 50:18.440
to approve you

50:19.070 --> 50:20.400
and not force you to retire when she got better.

50:20.400 --> 50:25.060
That's between you and Lieutenant Yoon.

50:25.110 --> 50:26.510
It has nothing to do with me.

50:26.930 --> 50:27.610
Seo Dae Young!

50:27.610 --> 50:29.040
I decided to choose Yoon Myung Joo.

50:29.720 --> 50:31.300
If I have to pay the price,

50:31.300 --> 50:32.720
I'll gladly do it.

50:33.750 --> 50:35.180
I'm going to leave the army.

50:37.050 --> 50:38.840
No, you can't.

50:38.840 --> 50:41.000
Let's talk. Come on.

50:47.810 --> 50:49.070
This is what I came here to tell you.

50:52.590 --> 50:54.160
Sir.

51:08.340 --> 51:09.710
How can you do this to me?

51:10.320 --> 51:12.040
How can you make me find out this way?

51:12.040 --> 51:13.460
I know how you feel...

51:13.460 --> 51:14.460
No, you don't.

51:15.550 --> 51:16.750
If you know, you couldn't do this to me.

51:17.740 --> 51:19.770
I made the decision not to break up with you.

51:19.770 --> 51:21.380
Do you think it was easy for me?

51:21.380 --> 51:22.390
It wasn't.

51:22.650 --> 51:23.660
I know.

51:24.640 --> 51:25.840
What about me?

51:26.540 --> 51:28.100
Do you think it was easy for me?

51:28.410 --> 51:30.180
I threatened my dad

51:30.180 --> 51:31.300
when my life was at stake.

51:31.940 --> 51:33.740
Do you think I'm proud of myself?

51:33.740 --> 51:35.690
Who asked you to do that?

51:38.730 --> 51:41.040
Because you keep running away.

51:43.490 --> 51:45.650
When I was fighting against my dad, where were you?

51:47.130 --> 51:48.830
Do you think I'm a joke?

51:49.970 --> 51:51.580
How can you decide something like this

51:51.950 --> 51:53.570
without even talking to me?

51:53.570 --> 51:54.400
I did!

51:54.400 --> 51:55.610
Numerous times!

51:56.290 --> 51:59.070
Every time I ran away from you

51:59.650 --> 52:01.850
and I couldn't answer your calls.

52:01.850 --> 52:03.790
I was talking to you at the top of my lungs!

52:06.420 --> 52:07.550
How dare you

52:07.550 --> 52:08.530
ask him a favor like that?

52:12.040 --> 52:14.020
I guess neither of us respected each other.

52:15.250 --> 52:17.020
We're not the same.

52:17.640 --> 52:19.110
I was trying to persuade my father...

52:19.110 --> 52:21.050
You made me feel small while doing it.

52:24.120 --> 52:26.410
I don't want his understanding. I want his approval.

52:27.240 --> 52:29.110
I wanted Commander Yoon  to choose me not because his daughter

52:29.110 --> 52:30.490
but

52:30.780 --> 52:32.420
because it's me.

52:32.990 --> 52:35.020
But

52:38.510 --> 52:39.890
if he chooses me

52:41.810 --> 52:43.730
because it was

52:44.920 --> 52:47.330
his daughter's dying wish...

52:51.660 --> 52:53.160
I couldn't be with you.

53:01.470 --> 53:02.980
Then don't be with me.

53:04.470 --> 53:05.850
Let's end things here.

53:10.570 --> 53:12.160
If you're going to be unhappy

53:17.020 --> 53:19.320
because of me,

53:21.520 --> 53:23.620
be happy without me.

53:24.010 --> 53:25.590
I mean it.

53:52.750 --> 53:54.650
Wow! We're finally watching this movie together.

53:55.960 --> 53:57.180
It took a while,

53:58.230 --> 53:59.770
but I'm glad that we came back to where we started.

54:01.190 --> 54:02.430
It took a while?

54:04.500 --> 54:06.340
Let's go back to

54:06.700 --> 54:07.900
the beach

54:07.900 --> 54:09.630
where we took a pebble from.

54:11.100 --> 54:12.120
Sure.

54:12.450 --> 54:13.420
Let's go back there

54:14.570 --> 54:16.160
together.

54:19.120 --> 54:20.410
Who is it?

54:23.220 --> 54:24.130
Please.

54:24.680 --> 54:25.730
What's happening?

54:27.610 --> 54:29.120
I have to go.

54:30.290 --> 54:31.390
Now?

54:31.390 --> 54:33.190
Yes, I'm sorry.

54:35.310 --> 54:37.030
Are you standing me up now?

54:37.660 --> 54:39.270
I'm sorry. It's an emergency.

54:39.270 --> 54:40.960
Let's watch this movie together next time.

54:40.960 --> 54:42.600
Why don't we leave together?

54:43.570 --> 54:46.150
No.I'm going to watch it on my own.

54:46.150 --> 54:47.030
Go on.

54:54.580 --> 54:57.290
That only works on the first date.

54:57.290 --> 54:59.030
I paid for it. I want to watch it too.

54:59.460 --> 55:00.510
Get up! Now!

55:03.190 --> 55:04.100
Geeze.

55:04.850 --> 55:05.900
I thought it'd work.

55:07.870 --> 55:09.140
When are we going to watch this movie?

55:12.910 --> 55:14.260
At the second North and South Talks,

55:14.260 --> 55:15.430
which will be held at the Seoul Hotel

55:15.430 --> 55:17.410
at 13:00 on Thursday,

55:17.410 --> 55:18.860
the PSS will escort

55:18.860 --> 55:20.130
the VIPs at close range.

55:21.220 --> 55:24.660
The 707 Alpha, Bravo,

55:24.660 --> 55:27.200
and Charlie Teams will check the assassination points

55:27.200 --> 55:30.540
of the conference hall
on the seventeenth floor

55:30.540 --> 55:32.450
and guard the area around the venue.

55:33.070 --> 55:35.930
The leader of Alpha Team will be in charge of

55:35.930 --> 55:37.360
the drill today and the security of the venue.

55:46.140 --> 55:47.420
Everyone! Listen up!

55:47.420 --> 55:48.880
Until the rehearsal vehicles get here,

55:48.880 --> 55:49.710
take five.

55:50.450 --> 55:51.420
Over!

55:59.570 --> 56:00.520
Aren't you going to share?

56:03.910 --> 56:05.240
It's not enough to share.

56:05.750 --> 56:06.940
Did you only buy one?

56:06.940 --> 56:08.360
I bought two, but I already finished the first one.

56:08.800 --> 56:09.840
I'm craving something sweet.

56:10.220 --> 56:11.250
I think I'm depressed.

56:12.560 --> 56:15.100
You get depressed for no reason.

56:15.100 --> 56:16.560
I broke up with Myung Joo.

56:19.130 --> 56:20.130
What?

56:22.320 --> 56:23.400
Why?

56:23.790 --> 56:24.730
Who dumped whom?

56:24.730 --> 56:25.720
She dumped me,

56:26.390 --> 56:27.930
but I can't tell you the reason...

56:44.380 --> 56:45.570
An ambulance is coming in.

56:45.570 --> 56:46.510
Let's go.

56:57.670 --> 56:58.900
We gave two liters of saline on the way over.

56:58.900 --> 57:01.060
BP is 80. Over 50 Multiple gunshot wounds.

57:01.060 --> 57:02.420
Gunshot wounds?

57:04.600 --> 57:06.430
Get an X-ray and send him to the OR.

57:10.500 --> 57:11.410
Call the CS department.

57:11.410 --> 57:12.520
I'm here.

57:12.520 --> 57:13.500
Go check the other patient.

57:16.350 --> 57:17.360
What have we got?

57:17.870 --> 57:18.790
Ah?

58:06.020 --> 58:11.190
-=Next Episode-=

58:11.930 --> 58:14.860
Your silly joke doesn't make me feel better.

58:15.600 --> 58:17.290
I'm worried sick.

58:29.080 --> 58:30.880
Don't worry about me.

58:31.650 --> 58:33.000
I'll be fine.

58:36.750 --> 58:38.850
Please take good care of Captain Yoo.

58:39.840 --> 58:42.620
I really, really like him.

58:43.020 --> 58:45.040
I'll tell him when he comes back.
